    "-Min-score: This represents the minimum score that an individual must achieve for the TLO to be considered complete.",
    "System DesignOur system design is based on generating cyber exercise scenarios using two LLMs in parallel.",
    "LLM1 acts as the Chief Information Security Officer (CISO) of the organization and possesses knowledge about the organization, while the second LLM is a security expert well-informed about the current cyber environment 3.",
